{"tid":1501661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果想自殺，有咩死法/做啲咩可以死得有價值啲？","createTime":"2019-08-24T12:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:08:07.000Z","uid":82880,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1501deb0cb1b7bf325a820124c370521259cf581","tid":1501661,"uid":82880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"利伸唔係義士冇上過前線，唔係香港既現況令我絕望到想死，只係一啲私人原因再加情緒病令我不時有自殺既想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時會諗橫死掂死，如果可以做啲對其他人/社會有幫助，但冇人敢做既野（e.g. 攬住啲高官同歸於盡）再死既話好似會抵啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，有冇啲實際可行既野可以死之前/死既時候做等自己條命可以有價值啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5babea89d649917a45d373fd2c82a59cdbf617f6","tid":1501661,"uid":130177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"關關難過關關過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自殺就唔好啦<br />\n想做啲嘢就出嚟幫手"},{"pid":"d68baa71a2199f1b3656ad786fc77845844aff26","tid":1501661,"uid":26324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"殺休班警"},{"pid":"cd2a19e4ef441e9353ebc586cfcf7ca97b093825","tid":1501661,"uid":199487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"老死"},{"pid":"bdaeee3fc004eb0dbfc2514442ed5a6ff50575d9","tid":1501661,"uid":199501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:24:19.000Z","msg":"接汪汪放工/淋病"},{"pid":"f6666ffe085ee8ebaf35ba57391e4f861cfdc83e","tid":1501661,"uid":81914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"算吧啦你  食個飯好訓喇"},{"pid":"a8334f34787fa7aac5e39401d4f740b0cc07b0ce","tid":1501661,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"淋病+班狗官記者會時自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1914f1cae30ae8be003f0e262fda97b14f